{"id": "1488863620443013130", "channel_id": "1488863620443013130", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "锵锵——！\n哎呀，各位真的去选课了吗？\n（小N假模假样抹了半秒眼泪，随即绽放出灿烂的笑容。）\n很遗憾——这套选课系统，是小N私自架设的。\n教务处从头到尾什么都不知道哦！\n规则里可从来没写过\"4月1日的公告必须来自校方\"吧？\n看在你们让我看了一出极好的表演份上\n选了课的各位，这节课就由我代劳了\n\n*愚人节快乐。*\n*——小「N」*\n\n***【教务处声明】***\n\n本处未发布任何选课公告。如有同学已填写个人信息，请前往信息安全处备案。我们已经派遣调查小队前往解决所谓的选课系统，该系统预计将于4月3日12:00下线\n\n*——拉蒙娜*\n\n请查收【弥萨格的道歉函】\n\n【弥萨格的道歉函】：JFQJ-VKUR-KZUY\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nHey there~!\nOh wow. You actually went and signed up for classes?\n(Little N pretended to wipe away a tear for half a second before breaking into a brilliant smile.)\nUnfortunately... this course selection system was built by Little N. Entirely on his own.\nThe registrar's office has been completely in the dark from start to finish.\nAnd nowhere in the rules does it say \"April 1st announcements have to come from the school,\" does it?\nIn honor of the spectacular performance you've all put on for me:\nFor everyone enrolled in these classes, I'll be taking over today's lesson.\n\n*Happy April Fools' Day.\n— Little \"N\"*\n\n***[Academic Affairs Office Statement]***\n\nNo course selection announcements have been issued by us. Any students who have already submitted personal information are asked to report to the Information Security Office immediately. We have dispatched an investigation team to address the unauthorized course selection system, which is expected to be taken offline at 12:00 on April 3rd.\n\n*— Ramona*\n\nPlease find the [Mythag Apology Letter] enclosed below.\n\n[Mythag Apology Letter]: JFQJ-VKUR-KZUY", "timestamp": "2026-04-01T11:32:28.862000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-01T11:33:22.060000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "shock2", "emoji_id": "1356085825829343344", "count": 16}], "attachments": [{"id": "1488863621076357221", "filename": "e6b4c024476148bb9d0bedd14b98f9f8.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 893699, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1488863620443013130/1488863621076357221/e6b4c024476148bb9d0bedd14b98f9f8.png?ex=69ce53cd&is=69cd024d&hm=8775f52535a8d7877449a3b7cf03d2672c42d830dcb14b09bd8a373726326ef6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1488863620443013130", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【教L̸o̸a̸d̸i̸n̸g̸.̸.̸.̸系□□□□???0x000告】——[TeachingL̸o̸a̸d̸i̸n̸g̸.̸.̸.̸System□□□□???0x000Notice]", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
